				<td colspan="2"><span>Not sure if 'delay' is a command, I use 'pause' the pause value is in tenths of a second, so you need around 30 in there, I think my macros use 28.. but then I don't use them much now.. too many missed notes:( 
<br />

<br />
I do remember that the most songs you can single macro is 3..
<br />

<br />
Oh yes..pause is the only command you can double up on one line<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
