				<td colspan="2"><span>Forgot one thing I would suggest you do the following:
<br />

<br />
/stopsong
<br />
/cast 1
<br />
/stopsong, /pause 28-30
<br />
/cast 2
<br />

<br />
This works better as a twist since the pause command can only be used once on a hot key at least in this setup.  For your setup you would have to do this:
<br />

<br />
/cast 1
<br />
/stopsong, /pause 28-30
<br />
/cast 2
<br />
/pause 28-30
<br />
/stopsong
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps.</span></td>
